DOCKER FILE FOR HTTPD, NGINX AND PYTHON APPLICATION

following below steps to do all those 
code---->Dockerfile----->build this Dockerfile------->image will be created----->if we run the image container will be created

RUN ------------> this component is used to execute the commands while creating an image
EX: docker build -t imagename:version .
CMD ------------> this component is used to execute the commands while creating a container
EX: docker run -itd --name containername imagename:version

Dockerfile----------> if we build this Dockerfile IMAGE will be created ------------>if we run this iamge the CONTAINER will be created 
          <------>RUN                                                   <--------->CMD


